  <a href="<%= magic_link_login_path %>" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white rounded-md bg-btn-primary hover:bg-btn-primary-hover active:bg-btn-primary-active transition-colors">
    新しいリンクを送信
